                "title": "Overhauled Audio Engine ",
                "desc": "Babylon.js 8.0 brings an entirely refreshed audio engine. It was designed to be powerful â€” taking advantage of the full suite of web-audio features, modern â€” class names and architecture you've come to expect, and simple-to-use â€” allowing anyone to leverage these features, no matter what your experience level.",
