                "title": "Gaussian Splat Updates",
                "desc": "Babylon.js 8.0 builds on the exciting foundation of Gaussian Splat support with some exciting new updates such as SPZ and compressed PLY formats, spherical harmonics, as well as runtime optimizations for memory footprint and CPU/GPU usage. ",
